{"tid":785914,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣冇乜朋友","createTime":"2018-08-19T15:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T18:01:06.000Z","uid":92792,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"84966d5f3f3903f9b43bb2dcffb437807c6d3e6a","tid":785914,"uid":92792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"中學畢業後，因為住得遠，又各有各忙，各有各生活圈子<br />\n之後漸漸都冇晒中學同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後因為班中學同學有共同興趣，又住得近，佢地幾個自己成日私底下約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到大學，雖然識到唔少friends但係好多都係hi bye friends，一放假就成日冇人約，好多時間都留係屋企<br />\n平時行街買衫都成日自己一個<br />\n食野又自己一個<br />\n做好多野都自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296d3ca71402eb92e92dff29c99040b408a31f19","tid":785914,"uid":145621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"習慣就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日俾屋企人串無朋友 慣晒了"},{"pid":"a5246a496a4b4176c620a82548125ba0156069a7","tid":785914,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"舊同學，舊同事都完全無聯絡"},{"pid":"d6ff07ab17b6356c1b6fb9828ad9ee07ab3aa5e3","tid":785914,"uid":176657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"慢慢就會慣架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d54c7c89cf1e38b23ed79bc6682965f0a97a29","tid":785914,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"就算生日,我都係一個人去海洋公園.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒放假就一個人去離島影相"},{"pid":"3a81418d598df8f1b1e309926a9ad0a3179e5834","tid":785914,"uid":202372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"我啲朋友&hellip;